-- Six Companies Submit Bids for Seven Sao Tome and Principe Oil Blocks
-- B y   K a t y a   A r a g a o
-- 2010-11-23T16:08:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/six-companies-submit-bids-for-seven-sao-tome-and-principe-oil-blocks.html
Six companies, including Nigeria’s
Oranto Petroleum Ltd. and closely held Afex Global Ltd., have
submitted bids for seven oil blocks off the coast of Sao Tome
and Principe, according to the country’s National Oil Agency.  Force Petroleum, Grupo Gema S.A. and Nigeria’s Overt Energy
Ltd. also submitted bids, according to a statement handed to
reporters in Sao Tome yesterday. The government will “soon”
announce the start date for the tenders, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  